# Daily Habit Tracker Update Walkthrough

## New Features & Changes
### 1. Notification Toggle Fix 🐛
- **Issue**: "Turn On" button was unresponsive or failing silently.
- **Fixes**:
    - **Codebase**: Refactored [utils.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/src/utils.js) to use consistent static imports for `LocalNotifications`, preventing initialization issues.
    - **Build**: Fixed a silent build failure by downgrading the compile target to `es2015`, ensuring all code is properly generated in the APK.
    - **Permissions**: Verified [AndroidManifest.xml](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EC%8A%A4%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98%EC%9B%B9%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4/daily-habit-tracker/android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml) includes `POST_NOTIFICATIONS` and `SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM` for Android 13+.
- **Result**: "Turn On" should now correctly request permissions (if needed) and schedule the notification. If it fails, a detailed error toast will appear.

### 2. Reset Day Persistence 🏆
- **Functionality**: Resetting daily progress preserves your "Perfect Day" count.
- **Verification**: This was implemented previously but might have been missing from the last APK due to build issues. It is NOW confirmed to be in the build.

